ygData.msgSnippet: It tells you.  The one I used to build skill was the trap at the entrance to Sol A.  I was successful disarming the trap every single time from lowest skill
ygData.messageBody:
It tells you. The one I used to build skill was the trap at the entrance to
Sol A. I was successful disarming the trap every single time from lowest
skill level til I maxed it at 100. Took about 5 minutes of continuous
clicking to bring skill all the way up.

Anthem Dirgemaker
Level 40 bard of Qeynos
Solusek Ro
